// Algorithm simply ek tarika hota hai mtlb ek-bundle ya Queue of steps hoti hai kisi kaam ko krne ka, jaise apn ek program banateh jo user se input leta hai koi html-code and phir voh user ko sirf-html-content deta hai, thus mtlb esa Program kaise banaya jayeh mtlb esa Program banane k liyeh apnko kuch koi tarika soch na hoga mtlb ess program ko apnko chote-chote chukde meh break krna hoga mtlb chote-chote Steps meh krna hoga , sochna hoga. ese Program ko banane k liyeh . thus toh yaha pe yeh tarika mtlb Steps ko hi simply Programming meh Algorithm bolteh hai ya bol dete hai.
